	Number = {153},
	Pages = {23-42},
	Month = {JAN-MAR},
	Abstract = {Social media influencers (SMIs) can be defined as a new type of
	independent actor who are able to shape audience attitudes through the
	use of social media channels in competition and coexistence with
	professional media. Being able to accurately identify SMIs is critical
