	polarizing topics of debate such as immigration, national safety and
	(Italian) nationalism. We found evidence of connections between Italian
	disinformation sources and different disinformation outlets across
	Europe, U.S. and Russia, featuring similar, even translated, articles in
	the period before the elections. Overall, the spread of disinformation
