	Organization = {Assoc Sociol Relig},
	Abstract = {Data drawn Rom a well-known survey of 2,667 registered U.S. Catholic
	parishioners (part of the Notre Dame Study of Catholic Pariah Life) were
	used to examine the ways in which black Catholics differ from white
	Catholics in the patterns - and predictors - of religious devotionalism
