	Pages = {43-53},
	Month = {MAY},
	Abstract = {The last decade has shown that sometimes even the largest online social
	networks (OSNs) collapse. Significant cascading mechanisms have been
	identified in the pattern of abandoning the OSN iWiW at its peak of
