	Month = {MAY 6},
	Abstract = {Inspired by the analysis of several empirical online social networks, we
	propose a simple reaction-diffusion-like coevolving model, in which
	individuals are activated to create links based on their states,
	influenced by local dynamics and their own intention. It is shown that
